Package: editrules
Type: Package
Title: Convert readable linear (in)equalities into matrix form.
Version: 0.3
Date: 2011-02-06
Author: Edwin de Jonge, Mark van der Loo
Maintainer: Edwin de Jonge <edwindjonge@gmail.com>
Description: Facilitates reading of linear (in)equalities, converting
    them into matrix format (and vice versa) and checking if data are
    valid according to these rules.  This package can be useful as
    input for automatic correction methods (imputation).
License: GPL version 3
LazyLoad: yes
Depends:
URL: http://code.google.com/p/editrules/
Collate: 'check.R' 'editmatrix.R' 'editmatrixAttr.R' 'pkg.R'
